    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend trip, this car is ready to hit the road with you. It\u2019s got plenty of life left and runs like a dream. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
