    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this E46-generation M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit maintains excellent compression and benefits from a recently serviced double VANOS system and rod bearing replacement. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise gates, feeding power to the rear wheels through a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally sound with documented rear subframe reinforcement already completed. Handling is crisp thanks to refreshed bushings and a well-sorted suspension that retains its original geometry. The individual throttle bodies provide the immediate induction response this chassis is famous for. While it shows the honest patina of a driven machine, the mechanical vitals and drivetrain synchronization remain robust, making it an ideal candidate for spirited B-road use or a dedicated weekend flyer.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
