    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior presents beautifully, finished in a deep gloss that still catches the light, though you will find minor, expected road wear upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with well-preserved upholstery and a dashboard free of any cracks or fading. Every electronic feature, from the ice-cold dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in great shape; the engine pulls strongly without any hesitation, and the transmission provides smooth, predictable shifts. I have stayed on top of all preventative maintenance, including recent oil changes and a brake service, ensuring it is ready for the road immediately. If you are looking for a dependable, well-cared-for car that offers a premium driving experience without the 'new car' price tag, this is the one for you.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
