      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! It has been such a reliable companion for me and is still in really solid shape. It\u2019s been well-loved, runs beautifully, and is totally ready to hit the road for its next big adventure with a new owner. Whether you're looking for a dependable daily driver or something for those fun weekend getaways, this one is a fantastic pick. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
      "price": 32000.0,
